Mission.Title: C7M8sanitizedfinal
Mission.Comments:
CAMPAIGN 7: NEOFEUDAL SANDLORDS MISSION 8: OHIO-CODED OTTOMAN ONBOARDING
Last week, we struck Incirlik and took the airbase there and our DAD operators contested Gazipasa. This week, we've got an emergency contract for Benzos, one of his top reseach folks got kidnapped on the verge of a major energy tech breakthrough.
We are contracted to get the VIP out of a secure facility marked on F10. Benzos' AI intel division indicates that the forces holding the VIP may try to kill him if they think they might lose him.
This is bad timing for us because we just finalized the terms to sell the thousands of pounds of synthcoke we took off of the superlab platform to a local turkish supremacist militia.
The buyers are extremely concerned that buying thousands of pounds of synthcoke from us might be a fatal enterprise. They have deployed numerous civilian vics to the coastal city of Mersin, marked on F10 as SELL COCAINE. The vics will not stop until one of our transport helos gets near enough to authenticate via the ancient "bluetooth" protocol, and they're not telling us which one truck is their guy.
Our transports are tasked with clearing out the city, finding the turkpremacist coke mule truck, then popping smoke for the heavy transports to ferry in large quantities of dope.
Contractor Objective: Rescue Benzos' researcher VIP from the secure facility marked on F10.
Company Objective: Sell as much cocaine as possible to the militia mule in Mersin.
Weather: 2 layers Scattered, 23degC, light wind Mission Local Time: 1800
